Metadata: Environmental Studies of Monterey Bay and the Central California Coastal Zone: Progress Reports July 1970-February 1971
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

A progress report for the first half-year of operation for July 1970 through February 1971 at the Moss Landing Marine Laboratories. A National Sea Grant project supported by the Office of Sea Grant Programs, National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration, U.S. Department of Commerce Grant No. GH-94.
